listOf_FuncAndArgLists: a list of lists like [function, arg1, arg2, ...], specifying the set of functions to be launched in parallel.
names: an optional list of names for the processes.
If this doesn't work, maybe the stuff you're returning from your functions is not pickleable, and therefore unable to make it through the Queues properly. """ from multiprocessing import Process, Queue if not listOf_FuncAndArgLists: return([]) # list of functions to run was empty.
